1
00:00:02,660 --> 00:00:06,168
You'll go to Mere. Collect my
son's bride. Take Elvina with you.

2
00:00:06,208 --> 00:00:08,368
- Why?
- She knows their ways.

3
00:00:08,408 --> 00:00:11,328
My mother wants to drive us apart.
That's why she is sending you.

4
00:00:11,368 --> 00:00:14,088
I've seen you look at
Elvina and her at you.

5
00:00:14,128 --> 00:00:15,808
It's not the way she looks at my son.

6
00:00:15,848 --> 00:00:17,328
- Sand wryms!
- Run!

7
00:00:20,448 --> 00:00:22,695
- You're alive.
- Abrecan is impatient to know if

8
00:00:22,720 --> 00:00:25,088
you'll help him become
Jarl of the Shieldlands.

9
00:00:25,128 --> 00:00:27,688
She'll not give you what you want. I can.

10
00:00:27,728 --> 00:00:30,448
The Warig. Their war
bands are coming together.

11
00:00:33,848 --> 00:00:36,168
This time, they mean to destroy us.

12
00:00:36,208 --> 00:00:37,608
All of us.

13
00:00:37,648 --> 00:00:40,288
I have a daughter to bury.

14
00:00:40,328 --> 00:00:42,928
You will release me, so
I can be Slean's bride.

15
00:00:43,488 --> 00:00:46,168
- Does your support for Rheda stand?
- It does.

16
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:54,074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

17
00:00:59,048 --> 00:01:02,368
Aaah!

18
00:01:19,688 --> 00:01:21,888
Aaah! Aaah-ah!

19
00:01:24,728 --> 00:01:26,728
Aaah! Aaah!

20
00:01:36,568 --> 00:01:38,568
Look at you now!

21
00:01:40,248 --> 00:01:44,048
Pig filth, scut for brains! You
should have learned to climb!

22
00:01:49,768 --> 00:01:52,328
Aaah! Aaah! Aaah!

23
00:02:05,888 --> 00:02:07,888
Fixed you, didn't I? Eh?

24
00:02:08,967 --> 00:02:10,967
That'll show you.

25
00:02:11,008 --> 00:02:13,008
You and all your kind.

